divs: Sighting Details I was outside sweeping my porch, and I happened to look up at the sky admiring the nature. When I saw what is best discribed as a floating boomerang bag like object only it was clear, and sort of like a plastic bag in the sky. Then when I followed it with my eyes it seem to just disappear than I did not see it again. Before that time I saw birds in the sky around it then when it came closer, and disappeared the birds were all gone to.
